## 🏗 STRUCTURE MAP

### Actual file tree
```
WinBoost/
│
├── .readmeAI                   ← AI context index. Never move. Never delete.
├── Optimizador.bat             ← Main script. Single entry point. All 4 phases.
├── README.md                   ← Human-facing docs. Badges, FAQ, phase table.
└── (LICENSE)                   ← MIT license (not yet in repo)
```

### Architecture pattern
Single-file sequential script. All logic lives in `Optimizador.bat`. No modules, no includes, no external dependencies. Phases run top-to-bottom in a fixed order.

### Enforced structure rules
| Section | Owns | Must NOT contain |
|---------|------|-----------------|
| Admin check block | Permission verification, early exit | Any cleanup logic |
| Banner block | ASCII art, version display, pause | Any system commands |
| Log init block | `LOG_FILE` variable, initial `>` write | Phase logic |
| System info block | `wmic` queries, variable population | Modification commands |
| FASE 1 | File deletion, cache clearing, cleanmgr | Network commands, registry, DISM |
| FASE 2 | DNS, Winsock, TCP/IP, RAM, TRIM | File deletion, registry optimization |
| FASE 3 | Registry tweaks, powercfg, sc, fsutil | DISM, SFC, file deletion |
| FASE 4 | DISM (scan → source detect → repair → cleanup), SFC | File deletion, network |
| Final screen | Space diff display, choice, shutdown | Any repair logic |

