## 🔍 SYMBOL INDEX

### Entry points
| Symbol | Location | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| Script start | `Optimizador.bat:1` | `@echo off`, `setlocal enabledelayedexpansion`, version var |
| Admin check | `Optimizador.bat:15` | `net session` test, early exit with instructions |
| Phase 1 start | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 100 | `FASE 1/4 — Limpieza profunda` header |
| Phase 2 start | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 190 | `FASE 2/4 — Red y rendimiento` header |
| Phase 3 start | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 240 | `FASE 3/4 — Optimizacion avanzada` header |
| Phase 4 start | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 295 | `FASE 4/4 — Integridad` header |
| DISM source detection loop | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 320 | `for %%D in (A B C ... Z)` drive scan |
| DISM repair logic | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 360 | Conditional `if defined BEST_SOURCE` |
| Final screen | `Optimizador.bat` ~line 420 | Space diff calculation, `choice /C SN` |
| `:fin` label | `Optimizador.bat` last lines | `shutdown`, `endlocal`, `exit /b 0` |

### Key variables
| Variable | Set at | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `VERSION` | Line 8 | Script version string (currently `2.0`) |
| `LOG_FILE` | Line 12 | Full path to desktop log file with timestamp |
| `LOGTS` | Line 11 | Timestamp from `wmic os get localdatetime` for log filename |
| `CURRENT_BUILD` | ~Line 75 | Windows build number (e.g. `22621`) for DISM comparison |
| `WIN_CAPTION` | ~Line 65 | Full OS name string from wmic |
| `WIN_BUILD` | ~Line 68 | Windows build number raw |
| `WIN_VER` | ~Line 71 | Windows version string |
| `SPACE_BEFORE` | ~Line 74 | Free bytes on C: before cleaning (for diff) |
| `SPACE_AFTER` | ~Line 415 | Free bytes on C: after all phases |
| `BEST_SOURCE` | ~Line 315 | Path to best install.wim or install.esd found |
| `BEST_BUILD` | ~Line 316 | Build number of best image found (0 if none) |
| `BEST_TYPE` | ~Line 317 | `wim` or `esd` — type of best image |

