## 📦 DEPENDENCIES

### Runtime dependencies (all built into Windows)
| Tool | Min Windows version | Purpose |
|------|-------------------|---------|
| DISM | Windows 8+ | Image repair |
| SFC | Windows XP+ | File verification |
| wevtutil | Windows Vista+ | Event log management |
| wsreset.exe | Windows 8+ | Store cache reset |
| powercfg | Windows Vista+ | Power plan |
| fsutil | Windows XP+ | NTFS / TRIM |
| wmic | Windows XP (deprecated Win11 22H2+) | System info queries |

> ⚠️ **wmic note**: `wmic` is deprecated on Windows 11 22H2+. If it stops working, migrate queries to `Get-CimInstance` via `powershell -Command`. The script currently uses `wmic` for `os get Caption/BuildNumber/Version` and `logicaldisk get FreeSpace`. This is the only known tech debt.

### Banned tools
| Tool | Reason | Alternative |
|------|--------|------------|
| Third-party cleaners (CCleaner, etc.) | Cannot distribute, unpredictable | Microsoft built-ins only |
| `format` command | Catastrophic | Never needed |
| `rd /s /q C:\` without subdirectory | Destroys OS | Always target specific subdirs |

