## 📚 DECISIONS LOG

| Date | Decision | Alternatives considered | Rationale |
|------|---------|------------------------|-----------|
| 2026-06-12 | DISM scans all drive letters A-Z for install.wim/esd | Only scan D-F | Users may have ISO mounted on any letter |
| 2026-06-12 | DISM uses highest build number image as best source | Use running OS build to filter | Higher build = more recent patches in image |
| 2026-06-12 | DISM /ResetBase included in FASE 4 | Skip it to preserve rollback | Irreversible but recovers significant space; matches cleanup goal |
| 2026-06-12 | SysMain disabled unconditionally | Only disable if SSD detected | Most users have SSD; complexity of detection not worth it; README explains HDD exception |
| 2026-06-12 | Log file goes to Desktop | AppData, temp, custom path | Desktop is always visible; users find it immediately |
| 2026-06-12 | Browsers killed before cache clean | Only clean if browsers closed | Ensures cache files are not locked |
| 2026-06-12 | wmic used for system info over PowerShell | Full PowerShell script | Faster process startup; wmic built into cmd.exe session |

